00:35:32.120 --> 00:35:33.950
periodical.

00:35:33.960 --> 00:35:35.670
The author was a woman missionary who

00:35:35.680 --> 00:35:38.349
had been left behind in a native village

00:35:38.359 --> 00:35:39.870
to take care of the church while the

00:35:39.880 --> 00:35:42.390
