00:35:52.720 --> 00:35:55.070
the people saw this. She said, 'I just

00:35:55.080 --> 00:35:56.830
shook it off and said, "In the name of

00:35:56.840 --> 00:35:59.349
Jesus, I plead the

00:35:59.349 --> 00:35:59.359
blood."'Did

00:35:59.359 --> 00:36:01.590
