00:37:10.760 --> 00:37:13.190
of Jesus Christ is precious because

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:17.270
of its song-inspiring power.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:19.030
In Revelation 5:9 it says, 'And they

00:37:19.040 --> 00:37:20.950
