01:48:19.200 --> 01:48:21.470
We're praying into it.

01:48:21.480 --> 01:48:22.709
What we're doing right now

01:48:22.719 --> 01:48:24.910
is we're praying into the revival,

01:48:24.920 --> 01:48:27.070
we're praying into

01:48:27.080 --> 01:48:29.470
the harvest. The

01:48:29.480 --> 01:48:32.990
harvest is birthed out of prayer.

01:48:33.000 --> 01:48:35.709
And we call the eyes to be flooded with

01:48:35.719 --> 01:48:38.070
light, for the

01:48:38.080 --> 01:48:40.709
eyes of the unbeliever have been blinded

01:48:40.719 --> 01:48:43.590
by the devil. And we say their eyes

01:48:43.590 --> 01:48:43.600
are—the

01:48:43.600 --> 01:48:46.110
harvest is plentiful and the

01:48:46.120 --> 01:48:49.190
eyes are flooded with light. For a

01:48:49.200 --> 01:48:51.470
flooding with light is coming on them in

01:48:51.480 --> 01:49:32.590
Jesus'name.

01:49:32.600 --> 01:49:34.670
Thank you, Holy Ghost.

01:49:34.680 --> 01:49:36.550
Thank you, Holy Spirit.

01:49:36.560 --> 01:49:38.150
Thank you, Lord.

01:49:41.960 --> 01:49:44.190
You can't be worried about

01:49:44.190 --> 01:49:44.200
those

01:49:44.200 --> 01:49:46.830
around you. Listen, I see there's

01:49:46.840 --> 01:49:49.710
people that will walk in a

01:49:49.720 --> 01:49:52.830
great level of the glory. And you'll have

01:49:52.840 --> 01:49:55.790
people that are just negative people

01:49:55.790 --> 01:49:55.800
trying

01:49:55.800 --> 01:49:57.270
to tell you, 'Well, you can't

01:49:57.280 --> 01:49:59.550
do that. We know who you used to

01:49:59.550 --> 01:49:59.560
be.'But

01:49:59.560 --> 01:50:02.550
you'll rise up in the days ahead with

01:50:02.560 --> 01:50:05.070
great victory and authority. Do you

01:50:05.080 --> 01:50:07.710
understand? And

01:50:07.720 --> 01:50:09.950
the Lord will shake the people who used

01:50:09.960 --> 01:50:12.150
to hang around you,

01:50:12.160 --> 01:50:14.110
the people who used to be influencing

01:50:14.120 --> 01:50:15.750
you. Sometimes you've got to have new

01:50:15.760 --> 01:50:17.430
friends.

01:50:17.440 --> 01:50:19.830
You can't take people having

01:50:19.840 --> 01:50:22.430
a small mentality into

01:50:22.440 --> 01:50:23.710
what you're doing.

01:50:23.720 --> 01:50:24.950
And you can't tell everybody your

01:50:24.960 --> 01:50:27.550
business;

01:50:29.720 --> 01:50:31.030
they'll talk you out of it.

01:50:31.040 --> 01:50:33.350
'Well, you know who you used to be.

01:50:33.360 --> 01:50:36.590
You know what you used to do.

01:50:36.600 --> 01:50:39.110
You are never going to walk that

01:50:39.110 --> 01:50:39.120
way.'Listen,

01:50:39.120 --> 01:50:43.150
that's my past and God's

01:50:43.160 --> 01:50:45.630
called me to do this, and I can't take

01:50:45.640 --> 01:50:48.830
you with me.

01:50:50.000 --> 01:50:53.390
You've got to shake some people off.

01:50:53.400 --> 01:50:54.990
Maybe it's people

01:50:55.000 --> 01:50:56.870
around you at church.

01:50:56.880 --> 01:50:58.110
They might go to church; they might

01:50:58.120 --> 01:51:00.510
be your social friends

01:51:00.520 --> 01:51:02.030
you go out to dinner with and they try

01:51:02.040 --> 01:51:04.430
to tell you, 'Hey, we don't see you

01:51:04.440 --> 01:51:05.870
doing that.'But God's put

01:51:05.880 --> 01:51:07.950
it on me.

01:51:07.950 --> 01:51:07.960
You've

01:51:07.960 --> 01:51:12.790
got to shake some old friends loose.

01:51:12.800 --> 01:51:14.430
I'm trying to tell you something by the

01:51:14.440 --> 01:51:16.430
Spirit of God. You've got to shake some

01:51:16.440 --> 01:51:18.230
friends loose. Maybe some family.

01:51:18.230 --> 01:51:18.240
I've

01:51:18.240 --> 01:51:19.950
got to do what God's

01:51:19.960 --> 01:51:21.670
called me to do.

01:51:21.680 --> 01:51:23.190
You may not line up with that and that's

01:51:23.200 --> 01:51:24.350
fine, but you don't have to be in my

01:51:24.360 --> 01:51:25.630
circle.

01:51:27.670 --> 01:51:27.680
So

01:51:30.160 --> 01:51:31.950
people from your old church

01:51:31.950 --> 01:51:31.960
or

01:51:31.960 --> 01:51:33.870
old friends might not be able

01:51:33.880 --> 01:51:37.590
to be in your inner circle anymore.

01:51:37.590 --> 01:51:37.600
You've

01:51:37.600 --> 01:51:39.550
got to say, 'Hey,

01:51:39.560 --> 01:51:41.550
that was good for then, but it's not

01:51:41.560 --> 01:51:45.670
good for

01:51:48.880 --> 01:51:50.430
now.'Our

01:51:54.440 --> 01:51:56.630
kids hung out together

01:51:56.640 --> 01:51:58.470
all these years, but you've got to

01:51:58.480 --> 01:52:00.190
know that God's calling you up to a

01:52:00.200 --> 01:52:01.710
higher level.

01:52:01.720 --> 01:52:03.270
And

01:52:06.520 --> 01:52:09.750
they don't want to go to that level.

01:52:09.760 --> 01:52:11.190
They like where they are.

01:52:11.200 --> 01:52:12.990
But God's

01:52:13.000 --> 01:52:15.550
put a fire in you to do something more.

01:52:15.560 --> 01:52:17.990
Not that you're better than anybody, but

01:52:18.000 --> 01:52:20.390
it's time for you to soar. And if

01:52:20.400 --> 01:52:21.950
they want to cluck around like the

01:52:21.960 --> 01:52:24.310
chickens, you can't be with the

01:52:24.310 --> 01:52:24.320
chickens

01:52:24.320 --> 01:52:28.310
when God called you to be an eagle.

01:52:28.320 --> 01:52:30.070
Sometimes you've got to let the chickens

01:52:30.080 --> 01:52:31.870
stay where they are and you flap your

01:52:31.880 --> 01:52:34.790
wings and say, 'Bye-bye, chicken.

01:52:34.800 --> 01:52:37.950
I'm out of here

01:52:37.960 --> 01:52:39.190
because I can't stay around here

01:52:39.190 --> 01:52:39.200
clucking

01:52:39.200 --> 01:52:41.270
around like a chicken.

01:52:41.280 --> 01:52:43.350
I'm going to soar like an eagle.'And

01:52:43.350 --> 01:52:43.360
you've

01:52:43.360 --> 01:52:45.750
got to go up higher

01:52:45.750 --> 01:52:45.760
because

01:52:45.760 --> 01:52:47.630
that's where the fire

01:52:47.630 --> 01:52:47.640
is

01:52:47.640 --> 01:52:48.630
at.

01:52:57.680 --> 01:53:01.750
And sometimes a fish tank, another

01:53:01.750 --> 01:53:01.760
metaphor,

01:53:01.760 --> 01:53:03.430
for instance, is sometimes you just

01:53:03.440 --> 01:53:05.430
outgrow the fish tank

01:53:05.440 --> 01:53:06.870
and you've got to go into a bigger fish

01:53:06.880 --> 01:53:08.270
tank.

01:53:08.280 --> 01:53:10.190
It's like whenever I graduated high

01:53:10.200 --> 01:53:11.590
school.

01:53:13.880 --> 01:53:15.790
The counselor said that I could

01:53:15.800 --> 01:53:17.710
skip a grade because I had so many credits.

01:53:17.720 --> 01:53:20.350
And my friends were saying,

01:53:20.360 --> 01:53:21.750
'Why would you want to do that? Don't

01:53:21.760 --> 01:53:23.390
you want to just stay and graduate with

01:53:23.400 --> 01:53:25.910
your friends?'But I was mission-minded.

01:53:25.920 --> 01:53:27.630
And I said, 'The whole reason you come is

01:53:27.640 --> 01:53:30.670
to graduate, to get it done.'So it

01:53:30.680 --> 01:53:32.630
didn't matter about the social part.

01:53:32.630 --> 01:53:32.640
I've

01:53:32.640 --> 01:53:35.390
got to get

01:53:35.400 --> 01:53:37.190
out of this because I've got something

01:53:37.200 --> 01:53:38.390
more for God for me to do.

01:53:38.400 --> 01:53:41.550
Don't stick around because of

01:53:41.560 --> 01:53:43.590
other people with

01:53:43.590 --> 01:53:43.600
small minds

01:53:43.600 --> 01:53:45.030
because you have something bigger on the

01:53:45.040 --> 01:53:46.830
inside of you.

01:53:46.840 --> 01:53:49.270
Don't allow small-minded people to

01:53:49.280 --> 01:53:53.150
influence a big-minded vision.

01:53:54.600 --> 01:53:55.710
A lot of times they think you're

01:53:55.720 --> 01:53:57.750
bragging. They may think,

01:53:57.760 --> 01:54:00.550
'Who does she think she

01:54:00.560 --> 01:54:02.390
is?'What's

01:54:02.400 --> 01:54:05.710
inside of me is bigger

01:54:05.720 --> 01:54:07.630
than what I can physically

01:54:07.640 --> 01:54:10.030
tell you.

01:54:16.320 --> 01:54:17.870
The Lord said this is just a stepping

01:54:17.880 --> 01:54:19.750
stone.

01:54:19.760 --> 01:54:21.430
He said, 'Brandon, YouTube is just a

01:54:21.440 --> 01:54:23.990
stepping stone. This is not

01:54:24.000 --> 01:54:26.950
your goal.

01:54:26.960 --> 01:54:29.550
This is to get you from point A to point

01:54:29.560 --> 01:54:30.710
B.

01:54:30.720 --> 01:54:32.990
This is the beginning of your

01:54:32.990 --> 01:54:33.000
ministry.'It's

01:54:33.000 --> 01:54:34.350
like Billy Burke prophesied over

01:54:34.350 --> 01:54:34.360
me.

01:54:34.360 --> 01:54:36.150
He said, 'Brandon, you haven't even

01:54:36.160 --> 01:54:38.510
entered ministry

01:54:40.200 --> 01:54:42.030
yet.'This

01:54:43.040 --> 01:54:44.390
isn't what

01:54:44.390 --> 01:54:44.400
God's

01:54:44.400 --> 01:54:46.430
called me to do. God told me to do

01:54:46.440 --> 01:54:48.270
it for a season.

01:54:48.280 --> 01:54:49.430
Most people go, 'Oh, that means you're

01:54:49.440 --> 01:54:51.990
quitting YouTube.'I never said that. I

01:54:52.000 --> 01:54:53.910
said, 'This is a season for what I'm

01:54:55.070 --> 01:54:55.080
doing.'It's

01:55:01.640 --> 01:55:05.590
to go from glory to glory.

01:55:05.600 --> 01:55:08.910
And just like I

01:55:08.920 --> 01:55:10.870
said I started, this means there's going

01:55:10.880 --> 01:55:12.910
to be something more because I'm not

01:55:12.920 --> 01:55:14.910
camping here.

01:55:14.920 --> 01:55:16.830
I know what he's

01:55:16.840 --> 01:55:19.190
told us even today

01:55:19.200 --> 01:55:20.390
in

01:55:20.400 --> 01:55:21.750
our prayer time cleaning the

01:55:21.760 --> 01:55:22.870
car.

01:55:22.880 --> 01:55:25.030
What did God say?

01:55:25.040 --> 01:55:28.030
What is he putting inside of you?

01:55:28.040 --> 01:55:30.430
And most people are not going to

01:55:30.430 --> 01:55:30.440
be

01:55:30.440 --> 01:55:31.910
able to handle it because they're not

01:55:31.920 --> 01:55:34.390
called there.

01:55:34.400 --> 01:55:36.390
You may be around people who are in

01:55:36.400 --> 01:55:37.630
ministry with you, and

01:55:37.640 --> 01:55:39.830
you start telling them your

01:55:39.830 --> 01:55:39.840
vision;

01:55:39.840 --> 01:55:41.430
they go on tilt because they are not

01:55:41.440 --> 01:55:44.830
called there. God called you there.

01:55:44.840 --> 01:55:47.430
So that is why I say you learn

01:55:47.440 --> 01:55:50.030
not to put all your stuff out for

01:55:50.040 --> 01:55:52.310
everybody to hear. Keep your stuff to

01:55:52.320 --> 01:55:54.310
yourself sometimes

01:55:54.310 --> 01:55:54.320
because

01:55:54.320 --> 01:55:57.310
they can choke on your vision.

01:55:57.310 --> 01:55:57.320
It is

01:55:57.320 --> 01:55:59.750
not for them to chew; they

01:55:59.750 --> 01:55:59.760
are

01:55:59.760 --> 01:56:01.230
choking on it. They get a hold

01:56:01.240 --> 01:56:03.470
of your bone when you have your teeth in a

01:56:03.480 --> 01:56:05.070
big steak, and they

01:56:05.070 --> 01:56:05.080
are

01:56:05.080 --> 01:56:06.310
not ready for it.

01:56:06.320 --> 01:56:08.470
They have baby gums and

01:56:08.470 --> 01:56:08.480
are

01:56:08.480 --> 01:56:10.030
choking on your vision because it

01:56:10.030 --> 01:56:10.040
was not

01:56:10.040 --> 01:56:12.230
meant for them to eat.

01:56:12.240 --> 01:56:14.190
So do not cast your pearls before

01:56:14.200 --> 01:56:16.190
swine. Keep

01:56:16.200 --> 01:56:18.550
your mouth shut and let God do what He

01:56:18.550 --> 01:56:18.560
is

01:56:18.560 --> 01:56:20.270
going to do in your life. You do

01:56:20.270 --> 01:56:20.280
not

01:56:20.280 --> 01:56:21.990
need them in the first place

01:56:21.990 --> 01:56:22.000
because

01:56:22.000 --> 01:56:24.870
they did not get you there,

01:56:24.880 --> 01:56:26.350
so do not be telling everybody your

01:56:26.360 --> 01:56:28.750
business. I tell little bits and pieces

01:56:28.760 --> 01:56:30.150
and see if they choke

01:56:30.160 --> 01:56:31.510
on it. If I see they start choking,

01:56:32.480 --> 01:56:33.710
I pull the meat out of their

01:56:33.720 --> 01:56:35.150
mouth because they aren't ready for

01:56:35.160 --> 01:56:35.990
it.

01:56:36.000 --> 01:56:38.950
Why? Because it was not meant for them

01:56:38.960 --> 01:56:41.190
to hear.

01:56:41.200 --> 01:56:43.510
God told you because your teeth are

01:56:43.520 --> 01:56:44.510
ready.

01:56:44.520 --> 01:56:46.030
He told you that you are called to do

01:56:46.040 --> 01:56:47.950
something. You have to know this:

01:56:47.950 --> 01:56:47.960
you

01:56:47.960 --> 01:56:49.630
are

01:56:49.630 --> 01:56:49.640
surrounding

01:56:49.640 --> 01:56:51.590
yourself with a

01:56:51.600 --> 01:56:54.190
bunch of baby porridge eaters, and God

01:56:54.190 --> 01:56:54.200
is

01:56:54.200 --> 01:56:56.230
raising you up to be a meat eater. You

01:56:56.230 --> 01:56:56.240
are

01:56:56.240 --> 01:56:57.670
ready and you are going to start

01:56:57.680 --> 01:56:59.150
feeding the babies. Do

01:56:59.150 --> 01:56:59.160
not

01:56:59.160 --> 01:57:01.390
allow the babies to influence

01:57:01.400 --> 01:57:04.430
the meat.

01:57:04.440 --> 01:57:07.470
Well, I am not ready. Well, that is you.

01:57:07.480 --> 01:57:09.830
But God has called me and chosen me for

01:57:09.840 --> 01:57:11.990
such a time as this. And you have to make

01:57:12.000 --> 01:57:13.350
sure that you are not clucking with the chickens,

01:57:13.350 --> 01:57:13.360
because

01:57:13.360 --> 01:57:15.190
the chickens will hold you

01:57:15.200 --> 01:57:17.550
back. Do

01:57:17.550 --> 01:57:17.560
not

01:57:17.560 --> 01:57:20.030
allow the chickens to keep you in

01:57:20.040 --> 01:57:23.950
the barnyard.

01:57:23.960 --> 01:57:25.710
You were just a wrong egg

01:57:25.720 --> 01:57:27.510
born in a barn. You are an eagle, and

01:57:27.520 --> 01:57:28.430
you are looking around, thinking, 'I look

01:57:28.440 --> 01:57:29.950
different, man.'There are birds

01:57:29.950 --> 01:57:29.960
out there that have

01:57:29.960 --> 01:57:31.990
really fluffy butts. I do

01:57:31.990 --> 01:57:32.000
not

01:57:32.000 --> 01:57:32.910
know what is going on with these

01:57:32.920 --> 01:57:33.870
chickens,

01:57:33.880 --> 01:57:35.990
but look at me; I have big

01:57:36.000 --> 01:57:38.510
long wings. And they are looking, saying, 'He

01:57:38.520 --> 01:57:39.709
looks a little different. I do not think he

01:57:39.709 --> 01:57:39.719
is

01:57:39.719 --> 01:57:41.230
supposed to be

01:57:41.230 --> 01:57:41.240
here.'Then

01:57:41.240 --> 01:57:43.110
you

01:57:43.110 --> 01:57:43.120
are

01:57:43.120 --> 01:57:44.230
flying

01:57:44.240 --> 01:57:45.270
out of the chicken yard. There

01:57:45.280 --> 01:57:46.390
is

01:57:46.400 --> 01:57:47.630
a

01:57:47.640 --> 01:57:49.150
turkey,

01:57:49.150 --> 01:57:49.160
and

01:57:49.160 --> 01:57:50.510
all

01:57:52.040 --> 01:57:53.270
of a sudden, you realize

01:57:53.270 --> 01:57:53.280
there is

01:57:53.280 --> 01:57:55.070
something different. All

01:57:55.070 --> 01:57:55.080
the

01:57:55.080 --> 01:57:56.550
dust is flying, and they

01:57:56.550 --> 01:57:56.560
are wondering what is

01:57:56.560 --> 01:57:58.390
going on. You

01:57:58.390 --> 01:57:58.400
are

01:57:58.400 --> 01:57:59.870
there

01:57:59.880 --> 01:58:00.950
and they start scratching

01:58:00.950 --> 01:58:00.960
in

01:58:00.960 --> 01:58:04.390
the chicken yard, and you

01:58:04.390 --> 01:58:04.400
realize,

01:58:04.400 --> 01:58:05.750
'Wow, that felt good

01:58:05.760 --> 01:58:06.950
to do that,'because

01:58:06.950 --> 01:58:06.960
I am

01:58:06.960 --> 01:58:10.990
made to soar like an eagle.

01:58:11.000 --> 01:58:12.390
All that dirt comes

01:58:12.400 --> 01:58:13.709
up and those chickens

01:58:13.709 --> 01:58:13.719
are

01:58:13.719 --> 01:58:14.830
freaking out. You

01:58:14.830 --> 01:58:14.840
go, 'It

01:58:14.840 --> 01:58:16.670
is time

01:58:16.670 --> 01:58:16.680
to eat.'The

01:58:16.680 --> 01:58:19.510
chickens are running.

01:58:19.520 --> 01:58:22.990
Bye-bye, chicken. Do

01:58:22.990 --> 01:58:23.000
not

01:58:23.000 --> 01:58:25.070
allow the chickens to tell you that

01:58:25.070 --> 01:58:25.080
you are

01:58:25.080 --> 01:58:29.670
a chicken when you are an eagle.

01:58:29.680 --> 01:58:31.390
Tell those chickens, 'I was born in

01:58:31.400 --> 01:58:33.030
here, but I am not raised like you, because I

01:58:33.040 --> 01:58:34.910
look different.'Glory to God! My beak is different.

01:58:34.920 --> 01:58:37.070
My talons are

01:58:37.080 --> 01:58:40.070
different. And I have been made to go high. You

01:58:40.070 --> 01:58:40.080
have

01:58:40.080 --> 01:58:41.350
been made here to pluck on

01:58:41.360 --> 01:58:42.590
this ground, and I am not here to eat

01:58:42.600 --> 01:58:46.630
worms; I am going to eat fish.

01:58:46.640 --> 01:58:48.910
You have to think bigger.

01:58:48.920 --> 01:58:51.790
You have to stretch your capacity. Do

01:58:51.790 --> 01:58:51.800
not

01:58:51.800 --> 01:58:54.870
allow yourself to be small-minded

01:58:54.880 --> 01:58:56.230
because of who you are hanging

01:58:56.240 --> 01:58:57.310
around. It

01:58:57.310 --> 01:58:57.320
is

01:58:57.320 --> 01:59:00.030
time to shake the chickens off and

01:59:00.040 --> 01:59:02.510
fly higher. Not that you

01:59:02.510 --> 01:59:02.520
are

01:59:02.520 --> 01:59:03.790
better,

01:59:03.800 --> 01:59:06.110
but do not get

01:59:06.120 --> 01:59:07.790
an arrogant attitude. Always stay small

01:59:07.800 --> 01:59:09.190
in your own eyes, but you have to think

01:59:09.200 --> 01:59:13.230
